    "Deep neural networks (DNN) and their derived models are essential to modern artificial intelligence recognition methods.",
    "Meanwhile, there are also hybrid models and experimenter-defined identification methods.",
    "As shown in Table 3, Chinese Sign Language Recognition technologies and methods can be divided into two stages: sign language recognition based on traditional technology and sign language recognition based on modern artificial intelligence technology.",
    "In the first stage (approximately from 2000 to 2011), HMM, SVM, and DTW were the mainstream technologies.",
    "Among them, HMM, widely used in speech recognition and handwritten font recognition, has been introduced into the field of sign language recognition."
  ],
